# Ensure all entities are connected.
# All Resources are linked to Applications, ProductModels, Locations, and Agents.
# All Applications are linked to ApplicationModules.
# All ApplicationModules are linked to Applications and Agents.
# All Services are linked to ApplicationModules/Applications.
# All NetworkInterfaces are linked to Resources and NetworkLinks.
# All NetworkLinks are linked to Resources.
# All TroubleTickets are linked to Services/Applications/Resources, Agents, and EventRecords.
# All TroubleTicketNotes are linked to TroubleTickets and Agents.
# All ChangeRequests are linked to Resources/Applications/Services, Agents.
# All EventRecords are linked to ManagedObjects (Resources/Applications) and ManagementSystems (Applications).
# OperationPlans are linked to Pre/Post Conditions.
# AnomalyPatterns are linked to TroubleTickets/EventRecords.

# This graph is dense and interconnected, covering various aspects of the NORIA ontology_extra_node_10.
